videos.description: In the final seconds of the first quarter, NC State's Kai Crutchfield crosses her defender and scoops home a shot in the paint to tie the game at 14-14.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Crutchfield converts at rim to close 1st quarter) 2020/02/24

videos.headline: Crutchfield converts at rim to close 1st quarter

videos.description: NC State's Aislinn Konig strips Haley Gorecki then gets the ball in transition and finishes with an and-1 layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Konig steals and scores for NC State) 2020/02/24

videos.headline: Konig steals and scores for NC State

videos.description: Aislinn Konig drives, draws an extra defender and delivers a quick no-look pass to Eliss Cunane for the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Konig dishes no-look dime for NC State bucket) 2020/02/24

videos.headline: Konig dishes no-look dime for NC State bucket

videos.description: Mikayla Boykin feeds a cutting Haley Gorecki, who gets undercut by a defender, but gets her shot to fall anyway for the hoop and the harm.
